title: Snap AI is disgusting
text:
Snap AI was introduced with an update, no one asked for that. It's permanently pinned unless you pay for premium. Inconveniencing people for a quick pay check is a disgusting business model. 
This has been mentioned to the company through reviews and emails and they refuse to do anything about this. Like many companies now, it's about money and not providing quality.

title: Gets worse with every update
text: Not having the ability to turn off everything related to quick add is atrocious. Your friends stories are with other random people's stories and no setting turns it off. Making users pay for the premium version just to get rid of the AI that no one asked for is absolutely criminal. Snapchat used to be amazing. Now it's another shameless money grab with features no one asked for. Bring back the old Snapchat
